      "title": "Madness Armor",
      "html": "<div class=\"mw-parser-output\"><h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Madness_Armor\">Madness Armor</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/w/index.php?title=Skyrim:Madness_Ore&amp;action=edit&amp;section=1\" title=\"Edit section: Madness Armor\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<p>Madness armor is a type of heavy armor. The armor and shield have the highest base armor rating for their respective slots in the game.\n</p>\n<table class=\"wikitable sortable striped\">\n<tbody><tr>\n<th rowspan=\"2\" class=\"unsortable\">\n</th>\n<th rowspan=\"2\">Name (<a href=\"/wiki/Skyrim:Form_ID\" title=\"Skyrim:Form ID\">ID</a>)\n</th>\n<th rowspan=\"2\"><a href=\"/wiki/File:SR-icon-clothing-Leather_Backpack_(square).png\" class=\"image\" title=\"Weight\"><img alt=\"Weight\" src=\"//images.uesp.net/thumb/2/2d/SR-icon-clothing-Leather_Backpack_%28square%29.png/22px-SR-icon-clothing-Leather_Backpack_%28square%29.png\" width=\"22\" height=\"22\" srcset=\"//images.uesp.net/thumb/2/2d/SR-icon-clothing-Leather_Backpack_%28square%29.png/33px-SR-icon-clothing-Leather_Backpack_%28square%29.png 1.5x, //images.uesp.net/thumb/2/2d/SR-icon-clothing-Leather_Backpack_%28square%29.png/44px-SR-icon-clothing-Leather_Backpack_%28square%29.png 2x\" /></a>\n</th>\n<th rowspan=\"2\"><a href=\"/wiki/File:SR-item-Gold-heads.png\" class=\"image\" title=\"Value\"><img alt=\"Value\" src=\"//images.uesp.net/thumb/5/52/SR-item-Gold-heads.png/22px-SR-item-Gold-heads.png\" width=\"22\" height=\"22\" srcset=\"//images.uesp.net/thumb/5/52/SR-item-Gold-heads.png/33px-SR-item-Gold-heads.png 1.5x, //images.uesp.net/thumb/5/52/SR-item-Gold-heads.png/44px-SR-item-Gold-heads.png 2x\" /></a>\n</th>\n<th rowspan=\"2\"><a href=\"/wiki/File:SR-icon-armor-IronShield.png\" class=\"image\" title=\"Armor Rating\"><img alt=\"Armor Rating\" src=\"//images.uesp.net/thumb/f/f0/SR-icon-armor-IronShield.png/22px-SR-icon-armor-IronShield.png\" width=\"22\" height=\"22\" srcset=\"//images.uesp.net/thumb/f/f0/SR-icon-armor-IronShield.png/33px-SR-icon-armor-IronShield.png 1.5x, //images.uesp.net/thumb/f/f0/SR-icon-armor-IronShield.png/44px-SR-icon-armor-IronShield.png 2x\" /></a>\n</th>\n<th style=\"border-left-width:medium; border-left-color:black;\" colspan=\"3\" class=\"unsortable\">Raw Materials\n</th>\n<th style=\"border-left-width:medium; border-left-color:black;\" colspan=\"2\" class=\"unsortable\">Delta\n</th>\n<th colspan=\"2\" class=\"unsortable\">Ratio\n</th></tr>\n<tr>\n<th style=\"border-left-width:medium; border-left-color:black;\"><a href=\"/wiki/File:SR-icon-ingot-Madness_Ingot.png\" class=\"image\"><img alt=\"SR-icon-ingot-Madness Ingot.png\" src=\"//images.uesp.net/thumb/0/0c/SR-icon-ingot-Madness_Ingot.png/24px-SR-icon-ingot-Madness_Ingot.png\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" srcset=\"//images.uesp.net/thumb/0/0c/SR-icon-ingot-Madness_Ingot.png/36px-SR-icon-ingot-Madness_Ingot.png 1.5x, //images.uesp.net/thumb/0/0c/SR-icon-ingot-Madness_Ingot.png/48px-SR-icon-ingot-Madness_Ingot.png 2x\" /></a> <a href=\"/wiki/Skyrim:Madness_Ingot\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Skyrim:Madness Ingot\">Madness</a>\n</th>\n<th><a href=\"/wiki/File:SR-icon-ingot-Ebony_Ingot.png\" class=\"image\"><img alt=\"SR-icon-ingot-Ebony Ingot.png\" src=\"//images.uesp.net/thumb/7/78/SR-icon-ingot-Ebony_Ingot.png/24px-SR-icon-ingot-Ebony_Ingot.png\" width=\"24\" height=\"20\" srcset=\"//images.uesp.net/thumb/7/78/SR-icon-ingot-Ebony_Ingot.png/36px-SR-icon-ingot-Ebony_Ingot.png 1.5x, //images.uesp.net/thumb/7/78/SR-icon-ingot-Ebony_Ingot.png/48px-SR-icon-ingot-Ebony_Ingot.png 2x\" /></a> <a href=\"/wiki/Skyrim:Ebony_Ingot\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Skyrim:Ebony Ingot\">Ebony</a>\n</th>\n<th><a href=\"/wiki/File:SR-icon-misc-LeatherStrips.png\" class=\"image\"><img alt=\"SR-icon-misc-LeatherStrips.png\" src=\"//images.uesp.net/thumb/3/3a/SR-icon-misc-LeatherStrips.png/24px-SR-icon-misc-LeatherStrips.png\" wi