    "4": {
      "title": "Madness Weapons",
      "html": "<div class=\"mw-parser-output\"><h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Madness_Weapons\">Madness Weapons</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/w/index.php?title=Skyrim:Madness_Ore&amp;action=edit&amp;section=1\" title=\"Edit section: Madness Weapons\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<div class=\"thumb tright\"><div class=\"thumbinner\" style=\"width:202px;\"><a href=\"/wiki/File:SR-item-Madness_Weapons.jpg\" class=\"image\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"//images.uesp.net/thumb/8/89/SR-item-Madness_Weapons.jpg/200px-SR-item-Madness_Weapons.jpg\" width=\"200\" height=\"150\" class=\"thumbimage\" srcset=\"//images.uesp.net/thumb/8/89/SR-item-Madness_Weapons.jpg/300px-SR-item-Madness_Weapons.jpg 1.5x, //images.uesp.net/thumb/8/89/SR-item-Madness_Weapons.jpg/400px-SR-item-Madness_Weapons.jpg 2x\" /></a>  <div class=\"thumbcaption\"><div class=\"magnify\"><a href=\"/wiki/File:SR-item-Madness_Weapons.jpg\" class=\"internal\" title=\"Enlarge\"></a></div>Madness Weapons</div></div></div>\n<p>Madness weapons are better than <a href=\"/wiki/Skyrim:Dragonbone\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Skyrim:Dragonbone\">dragonbone</a> weapons, but are slightly heavier.\n</p>\n<table class=\"wikitable sortable\">\n<tbody><tr>\n<th rowspan=\"2\">Name\n</th>\n<th rowspan=\"2\">ID\n</th>\n<th rowspan=\"2\"><a href=\"/wiki/File:SR-icon-clothing-Leather_Backpack_(square).png\" class=\"image\" title=\"Weight\"><img alt=\"Weight\" src=\"//images.uesp.net/thumb/2/2d/SR-icon-clothing-Leather_Backpack_%28square%29.png/22px-SR-icon-clothing-Leather_Backpack_%28square%29.png\" width=\"22\" height=\"22\" srcset=\"//images.uesp.net/thumb/2/2d/SR-icon-clothing-Leather_Backpack_%28square%29.png/33px-SR-icon-clothing-Leather_Backpack_%28square%29.png 1.5x, //images.uesp.net/thumb/2/2d/SR-icon-clothing-Leather_Backpack_%28square%29.png/44px-SR-icon-clothing-Leather_Backpack_%28square%29.png 2x\" /></a>\n</th>\n